name: JKskirt
description:
Training with AOM3a3
It should be able to generate more stable textures of plaid, but it can be difficult to control, so please pay attention to the weights.
The ideal weight is 0.4~0.7
Sometimes, it may be better not to use this Lora.


Although it can generate many colors, it is better at generating red.
Basic Prompt:
red skirt, red bowtie,
(plaid skirt is optional prompt)
